            <p><strong>Your privacy is important to us.</strong> All processing for both the Free and AI Hashtag Generators happens locally in your web browser. We do not send your keywords, captions, or generated hashtags to any server, and we do not store this data. You can use our tools with complete confidence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">How can a hashtag generator improve my social media reach? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Using the right hashtags acts like a <strong>discovery engine</strong> for your content. They help categorize your posts, making them visible to users who follow or search for those terms. This can lead to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Increased impressions from non-followers.</li>
              <li>Higher engagement rates from interested users.</li>
              <li>Faster growth of a targeted, relevant audience.</li>
            </ul>
